schemaVersion: 1
id: course-factory-root
name: Course Factory
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  A complete online-course OS in a directory. Fill in three placeholders (who
  you are, what the course teaches, format + price), run the bootstrap prompt,
  and a course-creator agent builds your curriculum outline, an 8-module syllabus,
  drafts the welcome lesson, generates slide prompts, sales-page copy, and a
  launch-week sequence — plus a platform recommendation (Teachable / Maven /
  Kajabi / Podia / School / self-hosted).
entry: index.md
